~ start
do animation_player.play(&"walk_on")
do animation_player.animation_finished
I think it's about time...
Even if your father doesn't want me to, I must gather all the roses and form our long-awaited family.
do animation_player.play(&"walk_off")
I will defeat him to obtain the first rose...
=> END
